health
  max, regen
  reductions -- armours, resistances and evasion
mana
  max, regen, cost multipliers

stamina
  // stamina that drains during fighting/climbing/running/swimming etc. (activities), drains slowly, regens quickly while resting.
  max, regen (resting buff)
fatigue
  // debuff for stamina regen, max stamina, strength, intelligence, etc. restored by sleeping
  rises (depending on stamina drain and time)
